---
const PHONE = "+41793940167";
const symptoms = [
  { icon: "🔴", label: "Douleurs de dos" },
  { icon: "😣", label: "Tensions cervicales" },
  { icon: "💪", label: "Épaules bloquées" },
  { icon: "🔥", label: "Tensions musculaires" },
  { icon: "🤕", label: "Migraines et tensions associées" },
  { icon: "😰", label: "Inconfort lié au stress physique" },
  { icon: "🔒", label: "Sensation de blocage corporel" },
  { icon: "😴", label: "Fatigue physique accumulée" },
];
---
 
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-background">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-foreground text-center mb-4">
      Cette séance peut vous aider si vous ressentez…
    </h2>
    <p class="text-center text-muted-foreground font-body text-lg mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      La reboutologie s'adresse à toutes les personnes qui souhaitent retrouver un meilleur confort corporel.
    </p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-12">
      {symptoms.map((s) => (
        <div class="bg-card rounded-2xl p-6 text-center shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <span class="text-3xl mb-3 block">{s.icon}</span>
          <span class="font-body font-semibold text-foreground">{s.label}</span>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
    <div class="text-center">
      <a
        href={`tel:${PHONE}`}
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-cta hover:bg-cta-hover text-cta-foreground font-body font-medium text-base px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors"
      >
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 0 1 4.69 13a19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 3.6 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/>
        </svg>
        Parler directement au cabinet
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>